Dialogue: 100,0:00:04.98,0:00:06.69,Default,T,0,0,0,Split,Whoa!
Dialogue: 100,0:00:06.69,0:00:09.23,Default,T,0,0,0,Split,So this is what the seaside looks like in this world!
Dialogue: 100,0:00:09.23,0:00:13.36,Default,T,0,0,0,,Seeing a crowd like this really makes me want to mow them down, Miss Kobayashi.
Dialogue: 100,0:00:13.36,0:00:14.24,Default,K,0,0,0,,Don't.
Dialogue: 100,0:00:14.24,0:00:16.20,Default,Kanna,0,0,0,,Is the water here salty?
Dialogue: 100,0:00:16.20,0:00:17.78,Default,K,0,0,0,,Yeah, it is.
Dialogue: 100,0:00:17.78,0:00:18.91,Default,Kanna,0,0,0,,It's the same, then.
Dialogue: 100,0:00:18.91,0:00:22.54,Default,Lucoa,0,0,0,,I like how swimsuits give you a chance to strut your stuff.
Dialogue: 100,0:00:22.54,0:00:24.37,Default,K,0,0,0,,Uh, no. That's a bit out of line.
Dialogue: 100,0:00:24.37,0:00:25.54,Default,L,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 100,0:00:26.00,0:00:28.17,Default,L,0,0,0,,What do you think, Shouta?
Dialogue: 100,0:00:28.17,0:00:29.50,Default - Italic,S,0,0,0,,I-I don't know where to look!
Dialogue: 100,0:00:32.55,0:00:33.72,Default,S,0,0,0,,I feel so much better around you.
Dialogue: 100,0:00:33.72,0:00:35.97,Default,K,0,0,0,,I'm not exactly happy to hear that in this situation.
Dialogue: 100,0:00:35.97,0:00:37.55,Default,Security,0,0,0,,Excuse me, ma'am.
Dialogue: 100,0:00:37.55,0:00:38.30,Default,L,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 100,0:00:38.30,0:00:41.43,Default,Security,0,0,0,,Come this way, please. \NYour swimsuit is too risqué.
Dialogue: 100,0:00:39.68,0:00:42.35,Default - Top,L,0,0,0,,Huh? Hey, wait a sec!
Dialogue: 100,0:00:42.68,0:00:44.56,Default,K,0,0,0,,Saw that coming.
Dialogue: 100,0:02:16.99,0:02:19.49,Default,L,0,0,0,,Phew, I'm finally back.
Dialogue: 100,0:02:19.78,0:02:21.87,Default,K,0,0,0,,You had a spare swimsuit on you?
Dialogue: 100,0:02:21.87,0:02:23.58,Default,Lucoa,0,0,0,,I transformed my scales.
Dialogue: 100,0:02:23.58,0:02:25.54,Default,K,0,0,0,Split,Ah, I see.
Dialogue: 100,0:02:25.54,0:02:27.00,Default,K,0,0,0,Split,I'm guessing you two did the same?
Dialogue: 100,0:02:27.00,0:02:29.08,Default,T,0,0,0,,That's right! I looked them up on the Internet.
Dialogue: 100,0:02:29.08,0:02:30.00,Default,T,0,0,0,,Look good, don't they?
Dialogue: 100,0:02:30.00,0:02:32.84,Default - Italic,K,0,0,0,,Yeah, not so much the swimsuit as what's inside it.{the envy is real}
Dialogue: 100,0:02:32.84,0:02:34.88,Default,Kanna,0,0,0,,I wanna play already.
Dialogue: 100,0:02:34.88,0:02:37.17,Default,T,0,0,0,,Right. Let's play.
Dialogue: 100,0:02:37.17,0:02:39.13,Default,T,0,0,0,,What do you want to play, Miss Kobayashi?
Dialogue: 100,0:02:39.88,0:02:41.39,Default,K,0,0,0,,Whatever works.
Dialogue: 100,0:02:41.39,0:02:43.51,Default,T,0,0,0,,What's wrong with you today, Miss Kobayashi?
Dialogue: 100,0:02:43.51,0:02:45.47,Default,T,0,0,0,,You've been nothing but a spoilsport.
Dialogue: 100,0:02:45.47,0:02:48.81,Default,K,0,0,0,,Well, to be honest, \NI'm not really a big fan of the beach.
Dialogue: 100,0:02:49.85,0:02:51.27,Default,L,0,0,0,,There's such a thing as being too honest.
Dialogue: 100,0:02:51.27,0:02:54.36,Default,K,0,0,0,,I mean, it's hot, you get sunburned, \Nand the sand's irritating.
Dialogue: 100,0:02:54.36,0:02:57.53,Default,Shouta,0,0,0,combined,I have to agree. I'm more of an indoor person myself.
Dialogue: 100,0:02:57.53,0:03:00.07,Default,T,0,0,0,,Why'd we come here today, then?
Dialogue: 100,0:03:00.45,0:03:05.03,Default,K,0,0,0,combined,Well, you know, there's not much else \Nyou can do in the summertime.
Dialogue: 100,0:03:05.03,0:03:08.41,Default,K,0,0,0,,And on top of that, my boss{MD} asked me \Nto take Shouta out for some fun.
Dialogue: 100,0:03:08.41,0:03:11.29,Default,K,0,0,0,,So I figured we could all come.
Dialogue: 100,0:03:11.29,0:03:13.17,Default,T,0,0,0,,Oh, I know what's going on here!
Dialogue: 100,0:03:13.17,0:03:14.50,Default,T,0,0,0,,You're playing hard to get, right?
Dialogue: 100,0:03:14.50,0:03:15.71,Default,K,0,0,0,,Not at all.
Dialogue: 100,0:03:15.71,0:03:17.51,Default,Kanna,0,0,0,,I wanna play now.
Dialogue: 100,0:03:17.51,0:03:19.13,Default,T,0,0,0,,Oh, right.
Dialogue: 100,0:03:19.13,0:03:21.72,Default,T,0,0,0,,Then, uh...
Dialogue: 100,0:03:22.39,0:03:24.30,Default,T,0,0,0,,Let's start off by applying sunscreen!
Dialogue: 100,0:03:24.30,0:03:28.22,Default,T,0,0,0,,I can't believe your skin gets damaged without it. Such inferior beings!
Dialogue: 100,0:03:29.14,0:03:31.31,Default,T,0,0,0,,Here I go, Miss Kobayashi.
Dialogue: 100,0:03:31.31,0:03:32.65,Default,K,0,0,0,,Grope me and you're fired.
Dialogue: 100,0:03:32.65,0:03:34.11,Default,T,0,0,0,,G-Got it.
Dialogue: 100,0:03:34.11,0:03:36.86,Default,L,0,0,0,,Okay, Shouta. If you would be so kind.
Dialogue: 100,0:03:37.44,0:03:38.44,Default,L,0,0,0,Split,There.
Dialogue: 100,0:03:38.44,0:03:39.57,Default,L,0,0,0,Split,Go ahead.
Dialogue: 100,0:03:40.57,0:03:41.45,Default,L,0,0,0,,Come on.
Dialogue: 100,0:03:45.74,0:03:47.20,Default,S,0,0,0,,I-I can't!
Dialogue: 100,0:03:47.20,0:03:49.45,Default,L,0,0,0,,Really? Let's switch, then.
Dialogue: 100,0:03:58.30,0:03:59.88,Default,L,0,0,0,,How's this, Shouta?
Dialogue: 100,0:03:59.88,0:04:02.51,Default,S,0,0,0,,H-How do you mean?
Dialogue: 100,0:04:02.51,0:04:04.09,Default,L,0,0,0,,Am I applying it right?
Dialogue: 100,0:04:04.59,0:04:06.89,Default,S,0,0,0,,You really are a demon, aren't you?
Dialogue: 100,0:04:08.51,0:04:12.06,Default,S,0,0,0,,What are you trying to achieve by seducing me?!
Dialogue: 100,0:04:12.06,0:04:13.48,Default,T,0,0,0,Split,Lucoa.
Dialogue: 100,0:04:13.48,0:04:16.15,Default,T,0,0,0,Split,You might as well commit to \Nthe demon thing at this point.
Dialogue: 100,0:04:16.15,0:04:17.90,Default,Kanna,0,0,0,,I wanna play already.
Dialogue: 100,0:04:18.19,0:04:19.65,Default,T,0,0,0,,Next, let's split some {water}melons.
Dialogue: 100,0:04:19.65,0:04:20.40,Default,Kanna,0,0,0,,I'm in.
Dialogue: 100,0:04:20.94,0:04:22.57,Default,T,0,0,0,,More to the right.
Dialogue: 100,0:04:22.57,0:04:25.16,Default,L,0,0,0,,Too far! A little to the left.
Dialogue: 100,0:04:25.45,0:04:27.74,Default,T,0,0,0,,That's it. Now keep going straight.
Dialogue: 100,0:04:27.74,0:04:29.58,Default,T,0,0,0,,Okay, stop.
Dialogue: 100,0:04:34.75,0:04:35.63,Default,Kanna,0,0,0,,Yay.
Dialogue: 100,0:04:35.63,0:04:37.00,Default,T,0,0,0,,Kanna never fails to impress.
Dialogue: 100,0:04:37.00,0:04:39.13,Default,T,0,0,0,,She obliterated every last trace of it.
Dialogue: 100,0:04:39.13,0:04:41.13,Default,K,0,0,0,,Oh, whatever.
Dialogue: 100,0:04:41.13,0:04:42.76,Default,Kanna,0,0,0,,I wanna swim!
Dialogue: 100,0:04:43.05,0:04:44.76,Default,T,0,0,0,,Good idea. Let's go!
Dialogue: 100,0:04:44.76,0:04:47.01,Default,K,0,0,0,,Don't go into the open sea.
Dialogue: 100,0:04:47.01,0:04:48.72,Default,T,0,0,0,,Why not?
Dialogue: 100,0:04:48.72,0:04:50.56,Default,K,0,0,0,,It's not safe.
Dialogue: 100,0:04:50.56,0:04:54.39,Default,T,0,0,0,,Ah, that's true. Leviathan {\i1}is{\i0} pretty scary.
Dialogue: 100,0:04:54.39,0:04:58.02,Default,T,0,0,0,,I nearly got myself killed by him once.{ugh, this is some disgusting passive voice that I don't know how to handle} It was horrible.
Dialogue: 100,0:04:58.02,0:04:59.02,Default,K,0,0,0,,What'd you do?
Dialogue: 100,0:04:59.02,0:05:02.19,Default,T,0,0,0,,I called out to him from behind \Nthinking he was Rahab.
Dialogue: 100,0:05:02.19,0:05:03.90,Default - Italic,Lev,0,0,0,,You're dead, bitch.
Dialogue: 100,0:05:03.90,0:05:06.78,Default,K,0,0,0,,Right. Well, it's not about that. \NNo one can get to you if you drown out there.
Dialogue: 100,0:05:07.24,0:05:10.83,Default,T,0,0,0,,Oh, right. Humans can't breathe underwater.
Dialogue: 100,0:05:10.83,0:05:12.33,Default,T,0,0,0,,The inferiorities keep piling up.
Dialogue: 100,0:05:12.33,0:05:13.96,Default,K,0,0,0,,And you can, Tohru?
Dialogue: 100,0:05:13.96,0:05:17.79,Default,T,0,0,0,,You bet. It feels amazing \Nto swim to my heart's content.
Dialogue: 100,0:05:17.79,0:05:19.79,Default - Italic,K,0,0,0,,Do they have gills or something?
Dialogue: 100,0:05:19.79,0:05:22.92,Default,Kanna,0,0,0,,Lady Tohru, let's race to that thing.
Dialogue: 100,0:05:22.92,0:05:24.55,Default,T,0,0,0,,You're on!
Dialogue: 100,0:05:24.92,0:05:27.22,Default,T,0,0,0,,All right, Miss Kobayashi, give us the signal!
Dialogue: 100,0:05:27.22,0:05:28.55,Default,K,0,0,0,,Sure thing.
Dialogue: 100,0:05:28.55,0:05:30.14,Default,K,0,0,0,Split,On your marks...
Dialogue: 100,0:05:30.14,0:05:31.47,Default,K,0,0,0,Split,Get set...
Dialogue: 100,0:05:31.47,0:05:32.22,Default,K,0,0,0,,Go!
Dialogue: 100,0:05:33.98,0:05:36.69,Default,K,0,0,0,Split,I forgot to tell them to hold back.
Dialogue: 100,0:05:38.56,0:05:40.06,Default,T,0,0,0,,Not bad, Kanna.
Dialogue: 100,0:05:40.06,0:05:41.57,Default,Kanna,0,0,0,,Impressive as always, Lady Tohru.
Dialogue: 100,0:05:41.57,0:05:43.82,Default,T,0,0,0,,First!
Dialogue: 100,0:05:45.32,0:05:46.32,Default,K,0,0,0,,You went overboard!
Dialogue: 100,0:05:46.32,0:05:47.82,Default,Both,0,0,0,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 100,0:05:49.91,0:05:52.70,Default,K,0,0,0,,Well, let's grab some lunch for now.
Dialogue: 100,0:05:54.45,0:05:55.33,Default,Both,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 100,0:05:58.75,0:06:00.46,Default,All,0,0,0,,Thanks for the food!
Dialogue: 100,0:06:01.09,0:06:02.34,Default,Kanna,0,0,0,,What next?
Dialogue: 100,0:06:02.34,0:06:03.96,Default,T,0,0,0,split,Let's see...
Dialogue: 100,0:06:04.71,0:06:05.88,Default,T,0,0,0,split,Miss Kobayashi—
Dialogue: 100,0:06:06.67,0:06:09.30,Default,T,0,0,0,,What's the matter, Miss Kobayashi?
Dialogue: 100,0:06:09.30,0:06:09.97,Default,K,0,0,0,Split,Nothing.
Dialogue: 100,0:06:10.43,0:06:13.85,Default,K,0,0,0,Split,Just thinking that guy hasn't changed much over the years.
Dialogue: 100,0:06:13.85,0:06:14.85,Default,T,0,0,0,,Over the years?
Dialogue: 100,0:06:14.85,0:06:15.93,Default,K,0,0,0,Split,Yeah.
Dialogue: 100,0:06:15.93,0:06:19.98,Default,K,0,0,0,Split,I came here with my family when I was a kid.
Dialogue: 100,0:06:21.86,0:06:23.19,Default - Italic,T,0,0,0,,{\t(380,1330,1.5,\c&H000000&\3c&H000000&)}Family...
Dialogue: 100,0:06:23.61,0:06:27.11,Default,Father,0,0,0,,Kill... Kill... Kill!{tried some fancy stuff, didn't look too good}
Dialogue: 100,0:06:27.11,0:06:27.99,Default,K,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 100,0:06:32.03,0:06:32.91,Default,T,0,0,0,,Nothing.
Dialogue: 100,0:06:34.95,0:06:36.20,Default,T,0,0,0,,Miss Kobayashi.
Dialogue: 100,0:06:37.62,0:06:42.08,Default,T,0,0,0,,Could you tell me more about your family?
Dialogue: 100,0:06:44.05,0:06:45.38,Default,T,0,0,0,,Please.
Dialogue: 100,0:06:46.96,0:06:48.59,Default,K,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 100,0:06:49.01,0:06:51.72,Default,K,0,0,0,,I like to think we were \Na perfectly ordinary family.
Dialogue: 100,0:06:52.01,0:06:54.22,Default,K,0,0,0,,My upbringing was fairly ordinary.
Dialogue: 100,0:06:54.76,0:06:57.18,Default,K,0,0,0,,They even sent me to college.
Dialogue: 100,0:06:57.18,0:07:00.81,Default,K,0,0,0,,After that, I left my hometown to work.
Dialogue: 100,0:07:00.81,0:07:05.73,Default,K,0,0,0,,I call my parents every now and then \Nto let them know how I'm doing.
Dialogue: 100,0:07:05.73,0:07:09.28,Default,K,0,0,0,,Come to think of it, \NI haven't seen them in a while.
Dialogue: 100,0:07:11.03,0:07:14.24,Default,T,0,0,0,,Is that what a normal human family is like?
Dialogue: 100,0:07:14.58,0:07:15.24,Default,K,0,0,0,,Probably.
Dialogue: 100,0:07:15.91,0:07:20.25,Default - Italic,T,0,0,0,,How could she accept me, a dragon, given that?
Dialogue: 100,0:07:21.17,0:07:25.25,Default - Italic,T,0,0,0,,She had a normal upbringing \Nand now leads a normal life,
Dialogue: 100,0:07:25.71,0:07:26.96,Default - Italic,T,0,0,0,,so how?
Dialogue: 100,0:07:27.84,0:07:33.76,Default - Italic,T,0,0,0,combined,Does that mean the humans in this world \Nare accepting of dragons?
Dialogue: 100,0:07:33.76,0:07:35.26,Default,Father,0,0,0,,Kill them.
Dialogue: 100,0:07:35.26,0:07:37.10,Default,Father,0,0,0,,Humans are evil.
Dialogue: 100,0:07:37.10,0:07:38.85,Default,Father,0,0,0,,Massacre them all!
Dialogue: 100,0:07:38.85,0:07:40.39,Default,K,0,0,0,,What's wrong, Tohru?
Dialogue: 100,0:07:43.52,0:07:45.94,Default,T,0,0,0,,Oh, it's nothing.
Dialogue: 100,0:07:46.57,0:07:48.78,Default,T,0,0,0,,It's just, how do I put this...
Dialogue: 100,0:07:54.03,0:07:55.95,Default,T,0,0,0,,I'm starting to feel a little weary.
Dialogue: 100,0:07:58.95,0:07:59.95,Default,K,0,0,0,,Tohru.
Dialogue: 100,0:08:00.71,0:08:01.46,Default,K,0,0,0,,How about a ride?
Dialogue: 100,0:08:19.56,0:08:22.02,Default,K,0,0,0,,This really is incredible!
Dialogue: 100,0:08:22.02,0:08:24.56,Default,T,0,0,0,,It's been a while, so I'm going all-out!
Dialogue: 100,0:08:27.44,0:08:28.57,Default,K,0,0,0,,Hup.
Dialogue: 100,0:08:33.61,0:08:35.20,Default,K,0,0,0,,{Hey, }Tohru.
Dialogue: 100,0:08:35.20,0:08:36.95,Default,K,0,0,0,,Don't you get homesick?
Dialogue: 100,0:08:37.37,0:08:39.20,Default,T,0,0,0,,Not really.
Dialogue: 100,0:08:39.49,0:08:44.75,Default,K,0,0,0,,But talking about my parents earlier \Nmade me want to see them myself.
Dialogue: 100,0:08:44.75,0:08:47.59,Default,T,0,0,0,,I do wish I could see my parents \Nevery now and then.
Dialogue: 100,0:08:48.71,0:08:50.34,Default,T,0,0,0,,But I'm fine.
Dialogue: 100,0:08:50.34,0:08:51.21,Default,K,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 100,0:08:51.76,0:08:53.72,Default,K,0,0,0,,What's weighing on your mind, then?
Dialogue: 100,0:08:54.09,0:08:57.60,Default,T,0,0,0,,I was thinking about introducing you to my parents.
Dialogue: 100,0:08:59.81,0:09:01.27,Default,K,0,0,0,,Just do it, then.
Dialogue: 100,0:09:01.27,0:09:02.56,Default,T,0,0,0,,If only I could.
Dialogue: 100,0:09:02.56,0:09:03.18,Default,K,0,0,0,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 100,0:09:04.48,0:09:06.69,Default,T,0,0,0,,I'm sure they'd just kill you.
Dialogue: 100,0:09:08.69,0:09:10.40,Default,K,0,0,0,Split,That sounds pretty extreme,
Dialogue: 100,0:09:10.40,0:09:13.44,Default,K,0,0,0,Split,but I guess that's just how your world works.
Dialogue: 100,0:09:13.44,0:09:14.82,Default,T,0,0,0,,For better or worse, it is.
Dialogue: 100,0:09:15.45,0:09:21.45,Default,T,0,0,0,,From my parents' perspective, \NI'm probably the one who's out of line.
Dialogue: 100,0:09:21.99,0:09:23.45,Default,T,0,0,0,,It's sad.
Dialogue: 100,0:09:26.25,0:09:29.08,Default - Italic,K,0,0,0,Split,Whenever I talk to Tohru about these things,
Dialogue: 100,0:09:29.08,0:09:32.46,Default - Italic,K,0,0,0,Split,it feels kinda... depressing.
Dialogue: 100,0:09:33.88,0:09:38.93,Default - Italic,K,0,0,0,Joined,It drives home the difference between "communicating" and "understanding."
Dialogue: 100,0:09:39.72,0:09:43.39,Default - Italic,K,0,0,0,,It makes me realize that the worlds we've lived in are all too different.
Dialogue: 100,0:09:44.18,0:09:51.11,Default - Italic,K,0,0,0,,But maybe that's exactly why I want to treasure our time together.
Dialogue: 100,0:09:52.53,0:09:56.28,Default,K,0,0,0,,I think that shows you've become independent.
Dialogue: 100,0:09:56.61,0:09:57.78,Default,T,0,0,0,,Independent?
Dialogue: 100,0:09:57.78,0:09:59.20,Default,K,0,0,0,Split,Yeah.
Dialogue: 100,0:09:59.20,0:10:01.83,Default,K,0,0,0,Split,You've built your own, unique set of values.
Dialogue: 100,0:10:01.83,0:10:04.29,Default,T,0,0,0,,Does that mean I've become a grown-up?
Dialogue: 100,0:10:04.79,0:10:07.83,Default,K,0,0,0,combined,Who knows? I certainly don't.
Dialogue: 100,0:10:07.83,0:10:11.00,Default,K,0,0,0,split,Besides, most people don't grow up \Nbecause they want to.
Dialogue: 100,0:10:11.00,0:10:13.55,Default,K,0,0,0,split,Life just comes along and forces them \Nto stop being children.
Dialogue: 100,0:10:14.34,0:10:16.80,Default,T,0,0,0,,Oh, you've got a bite, Miss Kobayashi!
Dialogue: 100,0:10:17.63,0:10:18.97,Default,K,0,0,0,,There!
Dialogue: 100,0:10:22.39,0:10:23.56,Default,K,0,0,0,,It's so tiny!
Dialogue: 100,0:10:29.40,0:10:30.65,Default,K,0,0,0,,Should we head back?
Dialogue: 100,0:10:30.65,0:10:31.65,Default,T,0,0,0,,Sure.
Dialogue: 100,0:10:44.70,0:10:46.45,Default,Both,0,0,0,,Dragon fireworks?
Dialogue: 100,0:10:46.45,0:10:49.71,Default,K,0,0,0,,Yeah. I won them in a lottery \Nat the shopping district.
Dialogue: 100,0:11:02.39,0:11:03.51,Default,Kanna,0,0,0,,That's it?
Dialogue: 100,0:11:03.51,0:11:04.26,Default,K,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 100,0:11:04.26,0:11:05.26,Default,Both,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 100,0:11:05.26,0:11:08.31,Default,T,0,0,0,,That thing gives real dragons a bad name!
Dialogue: 100,0:11:19.90,0:11:22.24,Default,Kanna,0,0,0,,Wow! Amazing, Lady Tohru!
Dialogue: 100,0:11:25.87,0:11:29.00,Default,K,0,0,0,,Uh, I can't understand a word you're saying.
Dialogue: 100,0:11:39.72,0:11:41.68,Default,T,0,0,0,,What is this?!
Dialogue: 100,0:11:41.68,0:11:43.22,Default,K,0,0,0,,The admission line for Comiket.
Dialogue: 100,0:11:43.64,0:11:47.06,Default,T,0,0,0,,We're supposed to back up Takiya here?
Dialogue: 100,0:11:47.06,0:11:48.97,Default,K,0,0,0,,Help out, not back up.
Dialogue: 100,0:11:49.52,0:11:51.73,Default,K,0,0,10,,Two of his helpers suddenly fell ill.
Dialogue: 100,0:11:51.73,0:11:52.98,Default,T,0,0,10,,Piece of cake!
Dialogue: 100,0:11:52.98,0:11:55.40,Default,T,0,0,10,,{\q2}With my power, I can wipe out everyone here with ease!
Dialogue: 100,0:11:55.40,0:11:56.23,Default,K,0,0,10,,Don't.
Dialogue: 100,0:11:56.61,0:11:59.74,Default,T,0,0,0,,By the way, are you sure \Nwe should've left Kanna at home?
Dialogue: 100,0:11:59.74,0:12:02.74,Default,K,0,0,0,,A lot of stuff here isn't for the eyes of children.
Dialogue: 100,0:12:05.24,0:12:08.91,Default,Takiya,0,0,0,combined,Thank you so much, you two! You're lifesavers!
Dialogue: 100,0:12:08.91,0:12:11.54,Default,K,0,0,0,,It's the least I can do to pay you back.
Dialogue: 100,0:12:11.54,0:12:14.12,Default,T,0,0,0,,Didn't you ask Fafnir?
Dialogue: 100,0:12:14.42,0:12:15.13,Default,Takiya,0,0,0,Split,Oh...
Dialogue: 100,0:12:15.38,0:12:17.25,Default,Takiya,0,0,0,Split,He's doing his own thing in circle work.
Dialogue: 100,0:12:18.55,0:12:20.01,Default,T,0,0,0,,Circle work?
Dialogue: 100,0:12:20.30,0:12:25.80,Default,Takiya,0,0,0,,Showing and selling stuff you make \Nto like-minded people, like us.
Dialogue: 100,0:12:25.80,0:12:29.64,Default,T,0,0,0,,I see. But why would Fafnir do that?
Dialogue: 100,0:12:29.64,0:12:32.43,Default,Takiya,0,0,0,,I kept recommending new games and anime,
Dialogue: 100,0:12:32.43,0:12:35.02,Default,Takiya,0,0,0,,and he started drawing before I knew it.
Dialogue: 100,0:12:35.02,0:12:37.40,Default,T,0,0,0,,He's really enjoying life in this world!
Dialogue: 100,0:12:37.40,0:12:39.90,Default,Takiya,0,0,0,,Anyway, Kobayashi, I'd like you to handle sales,
Dialogue: 100,0:12:39.90,0:12:42.40,Default,Takiya,0,0,0,,and Tohru, if you could help manage the line.
Dialogue: 100,0:12:42.40,0:12:43.78,Default,K,0,0,0,,Sure thing.
Dialogue: 100,0:12:44.99,0:12:46.28,Default,T,0,0,0,,Very well.
Dialogue: 100,0:12:47.07,0:12:54.29,Default - Italic,Announce,0,0,0,,{\an8}The third day of Comic Market 90 will now begin.
Dialogue: 100,0:12:59.75,0:13:01.13,Default,T,0,0,0,,Wh-What's going on?
Dialogue: 100,0:13:01.63,0:13:02.88,Default,Staff,0,0,0,,Please don't run.
Dialogue: 100,0:13:03.97,0:13:05.51,Default,Staff,0,0,0,,Please don't run.
Dialogue: 100,0:13:05.88,0:13:09.76,Default - Italic,T,0,0,0,,They're all barely holding back their urge to run!
Dialogue: 100,0:13:09.76,0:13:13.23,Default,T,0,0,0,,Something powerful is suppressing their desires!
Dialogue: 100,0:13:13.23,0:13:14.48,Default,T,0,0,0,,But what is it?
Dialogue: 100,0:13:15.10,0:13:16.15,Default,Participant,0,0,0,,Your latest work, please.
Dialogue: 100,0:13:16.15,0:13:16.98,Default,K,0,0,0,,That'll be 1,000 yen.
Dialogue: 100,0:13:17.44,0:13:18.86,Default,K,0,0,0,,Here you go. Thank you.
Dialogue: 100,0:13:19.23,0:13:21.19,Default,Participant,0,0,0,,Your two most recent works, please.
Dialogue: 100,0:13:21.57,0:13:24.32,Default,T,0,0,0,,The end of the line for \N{\i1}Water Dragon Shrine{\i0} starts here!
Dialogue: 100,0:13:24.32,0:13:27.24,Default,T,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, could you all take one step forward?
Dialogue: 100,0:13:31.83,0:13:36.33,Default,T,0,0,0,,How are they so organized without any prior practice or rehearsal?
Dialogue: 100,0:13:36.33,0:13:38.46,Default,T,0,0,0,,There are tens of thousands of people here!
Dialogue: 100,0:13:38.46,0:13:41.63,Default,T,0,0,0,,They must be under the influence of something powerful.
Dialogue: 100,0:13:41.63,0:13:43.17,Default,Participant,0,0,0,,Um, excuse me.
Dialogue: 100,0:13:43.17,0:13:43.92,Default,T,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 100,0:13:44.21,0:13:46.26,Default,Participant,0,0,0,,Are you a cosplayer?
Dialogue: 100,0:13:46.26,0:13:47.59,Default,T,0,0,0,,No, I'm not.
Dialogue: 100,0:13:47.59,0:13:49.22,Default,Participant,0,0,0,split,Oh, really?
Dialogue: 100,0:13:49.22,0:13:50.55,Default,Participant,0,0,0,Split,Sorry about that.
Dialogue: 100,0:13:50.55,0:13:52.89,Default,Participant,0,0,0,Split,I was sure you were a cosplayer from abroad.
Dialogue: 100,0:13:52.89,0:13:55.43,Default,T,0,0,0,,I'll have you know I'm a real maid!
Dialogue: 100,0:13:55.73,0:13:58.81,Default,Participant,0,0,0,combined,Oh, I get it. You're in character.
Dialogue: 100,0:13:58.81,0:13:59.77,Default,Participant,0,0,0,,That's wonderful.
Dialogue: 100,0:13:59.77,0:14:01.77,Default,T,0,0,0,,No, no! I'm telling you I'm the real deal.
Dialogue: 100,0:14:02.07,0:14:03.98,Default,Participant,0,0,0,,Trust me, I feel you.
Dialogue: 100,0:14:03.98,0:14:07.03,Default,Participant,0,0,0,,If you don't mind, please let me \Ntake pictures of you later.
Dialogue: 100,0:14:07.03,0:14:08.86,Default,T,0,0,0,,Seriously, I mean it!
Dialogue: 100,0:14:12.87,0:14:15.37,Default,T,0,0,0,,The end of the line starts here!
Dialogue: 100,0:14:16.58,0:14:18.62,Default - Italic,T,0,0,0,,What a sweltering atmosphere.
Dialogue: 100,0:14:18.62,0:14:22.42,Default - Italic,T,0,0,0,,I feel like I'm in a firedrake's belly.
Dialogue: 100,0:14:22.42,0:14:23.96,Default,Clerk,0,0,0,,Thank you very much!
Dialogue: 100,0:14:23.96,0:14:26.47,Default - Italic,T,0,0,0,,I didn't expect it to be this intense.
Dialogue: 100,0:14:26.47,0:14:28.88,Default - Italic,T,0,0,0,,Comiket is a fearsome foe indeed.
Dialogue: 100,0:14:29.59,0:14:33.22,Default - Italic,T,0,0,0,combined/split,Seriously, though, just what is it that's attracting so many people
Dialogue: 100,0:14:33.22,0:14:37.27,Default - Italic,T,0,0,0,split,and keeping them under control?
Dialogue: 100,0:14:37.27,0:14:38.60,Default - Italic,T,0,0,0,,I don't get it.
Dialogue: 100,0:14:38.60,0:14:40.48,Default,Takiya,0,0,0,,Tohru!
Dialogue: 100,0:14:40.48,0:14:42.23,Default,Takiya,0,0,0,,Hey, you're doing great out here.
Dialogue: 100,0:14:42.23,0:14:43.94,Default,Takiya,0,0,0,,I've come to relieve you.
Dialogue: 100,0:14:43.94,0:14:45.19,Default,T,0,0,0,,I've been waiting for this!
Dialogue: 100,0:14:52.03,0:14:54.20,Default,Kanna,0,0,0,,Bug collecting...
Dialogue: 100,0:15:01.33,0:15:05.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Crunchy...
Dialogue: 100,0:15:10.26,0:15:13.14,Default,T,0,0,0,,Let's see... It should be around here.
Dialogue: 100,0:15:13.14,0:15:14.76,Default,K,0,0,0,,What are you looking for?
Dialogue: 100,0:15:14.76,0:15:15.76,Default,T,0,0,0,,Fafnir.
Dialogue: 100,0:15:16.14,0:15:19.27,Default,T,0,0,0,,I figured I could stop by during my break.
Dialogue: 100,0:15:24.02,0:15:26.23,Default,Fafnir,0,0,0,,One word out of you, and you're dead.
Dialogue: 100,0:15:26.53,0:15:29.15,Default,T,0,0,0,,You look like you're dead already.
Dialogue: 100,0:15:29.15,0:15:32.16,Default,K,0,0,0,,Well, this is how the first time goes for everyone.
Dialogue: 100,0:15:32.16,0:15:34.07,Default,T,0,0,0,,Can I take a look at your book?
Dialogue: 100,0:15:34.07,0:15:35.99,Default,Fafnir,0,0,0,,Do whatever you want.
Dialogue: 100,0:15:36.95,0:15:38.50,Default,T,0,0,0,,{\i1}Curse Anthology{\i0}.
Dialogue: 100,0:15:41.29,0:15:42.96,Default,T,0,0,0,,Th-These are...
Dialogue: 100,0:15:43.25,0:15:46.25,Default,T,0,0,0,,It's actually filled with effective curses!
Dialogue: 100,0:15:46.25,0:15:47.96,Default,T,0,0,0,,You've even listed how to activate them!
Dialogue: 100,0:15:48.34,0:15:50.72,Default,T,0,0,0,,If you read this, you could curse anyone to death.
Dialogue: 100,0:15:50.72,0:15:51.43,Default,K,0,0,0,,Come on now...
Dialogue: 100,0:15:51.43,0:15:52.80,Default,T,0,0,0,,{And for only }Only 1,000 yen! So cheap!
Dialogue: 100,0:15:53.14,0:15:54.80,Default,T,0,0,0,,This is a real steal!
Dialogue: 100,0:15:54.80,0:15:57.81,Default,K,0,0,0,,Uh, it'd be bad news \Nif that thing sold well and went viral!
Dialogue: 100,0:16:01.31,0:16:05.31,Default,T,0,0,0,,I didn't expect to see so many cosplayers.
Dialogue: 100,0:16:05.77,0:16:10.07,Default,T,0,0,0,,A good number of them are even dressed \Nlike creatures from my world.
Dialogue: 100,0:16:10.40,0:16:13.82,Default,K,0,0,0,,They're having fun playing characters from anime or manga.
Dialogue: 100,0:16:14.24,0:16:16.28,Default,K,0,0,0,,You're basically doing the same thing.
Dialogue: 100,0:16:16.28,0:16:18.58,Default,T,0,0,0,,I'm a maid through and through!
Dialogue: 100,0:16:18.58,0:16:21.71,Default,T,0,0,0,,No matter how you spin it, \NI'm your loyal sex slave!
Dialogue: 100,0:16:21.71,0:16:23.12,Default,K,0,0,0,,That's an insult to maids.
Dialogue: 100,0:16:25.50,0:16:26.54,Default,K,0,0,0,,What's up?
Dialogue: 100,0:16:27.17,0:16:30.09,Default,T,0,0,0,,The sahuagin, goblin, and witch over there...
Dialogue: 100,0:16:30.09,0:16:32.09,Default,K,0,0,0,,I see them. I wonder which work they're from.
Dialogue: 100,0:16:32.51,0:16:33.84,Default,T,0,0,0,,They're real.
Dialogue: 100,0:16:34.55,0:16:37.51,Default,T,0,0,0,,Those three actually aren't human.
Dialogue: 100,0:16:38.56,0:16:40.35,Default,T,0,0,0,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 100,0:16:40.35,0:16:42.60,Default,T,0,0,0,,You're from the other world, right?
Dialogue: 100,0:16:42.60,0:16:44.77,Default,Sahagin,0,0,0,,Oh, you too?
Dialogue: 100,0:16:44.77,0:16:47.40,Default,T,0,0,0,,Yeah. What brings you here today?
Dialogue: 100,0:16:47.73,0:16:49.94,Default,Witch,0,0,0,,We're here to kick back and have some fun.
Dialogue: 100,0:16:50.44,0:16:53.74,Default,Goblin,0,0,0,,Normally, we live our lives in our human forms,
Dialogue: 100,0:16:53.74,0:16:57.78,Default,Goblin,0,0,0,,but events like these let us take on our original forms.
Dialogue: 100,0:16:57.78,0:16:58.78,Default,T,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 100,0:16:59.24,0:17:01.33,Default,Sahagin,0,0,0,,This is a great opportunity.
Dialogue: 100,0:17:01.33,0:17:04.04,Default,Sahagin,0,0,0,,Why don't you let loose in your original form too?
Dialogue: 100,0:17:04.33,0:17:06.04,Default,T,0,0,0,,Oh, that's not happening.
Dialogue: 100,0:17:06.04,0:17:07.54,Default,T,0,0,0,,I'm a dragon.
Dialogue: 100,0:17:09.09,0:17:10.09,Default,Sahagin,0,0,0,,A dragon?!
Dialogue: 100,0:17:10.09,0:17:10.84,Default,T,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 100,0:17:10.84,0:17:12.34,Default,Witch,0,0,0,,One of those damn monsters?
Dialogue: 100,0:17:12.34,0:17:13.09,Default,T,0,0,0,,Uh, I guess?
Dialogue: 100,0:17:13.09,0:17:15.80,Default,Goblin,0,0,0,,Those things that only see us as food?
Dialogue: 100,0:17:15.80,0:17:16.64,Default,T,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 100,0:17:16.89,0:17:17.76,Default,Three,0,0,0,,Run!
Dialogue: 100,0:17:17.76,0:17:19.01,Default,Staff,0,0,0,,Please don't run!
Dialogue: 100,0:17:19.01,0:17:21.64,Default,K,0,0,0,,The dragons over there can get pretty wild, huh?
Dialogue: 100,0:17:21.64,0:17:22.89,Default,T,0,0,0,,They have the wrong idea.
Dialogue: 100,0:17:23.73,0:17:27.10,Default,T,0,0,0,,Dragons only eat as much as \Nnecessary to sate their hunger!
Dialogue: 100,0:17:27.10,0:17:29.69,Default,T,0,0,0,,Food chains, survival of the fittest, \Nso on and so forth!
Dialogue: 100,0:17:29.98,0:17:32.40,Default,K,0,0,0,,So you provide context instead of denying it, huh?
Dialogue: 100,0:17:32.40,0:17:35.03,Default,Staff,0,0,0,,You there, come with me!
Dialogue: 100,0:17:35.03,0:17:36.99,Default,Staff,0,0,0,,Your outfit is completely out of line.
Dialogue: 100,0:17:36.66,0:17:39.12,Default - Top,L,0,0,0,,Huh? Hey...
Dialogue: 100,0:17:36.99,0:17:38.62,Default,Staff,0,0,0,,Did you not read the guide?
Dialogue: 100,0:17:38.62,0:17:40.91,Default,T,0,0,0,,Lucoa is here too?
Dialogue: 100,0:17:40.91,0:17:42.37,Default - Top,,0,0,0,,Wait a sec!
Dialogue: 100,0:17:41.37,0:17:43.29,Default,K,0,0,0,,She never learns.
Dialogue: 100,0:17:43.70,0:17:48.25,Default,T,0,0,0,combined,Taking a closer look, there are actually \Na lot of people here in their original forms.
Dialogue: 100,0:17:48.25,0:17:49.17,Default,K,0,0,0,,What, really?
Dialogue: 100,0:17:49.17,0:17:50.04,Default,T,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 100,0:17:50.63,0:17:57.18,Default,T,0,0,0,,I mean, this world has always had stories \Nabout famous beings from our world.
Dialogue: 100,0:17:57.47,0:18:00.68,Default,T,0,0,0,,Take Fafnir and Lucoa, for example.
Dialogue: 100,0:18:11.73,0:18:14.19,Default,T,0,0,0,,Uh, I...
Dialogue: 100,0:18:20.32,0:18:23.99,Default,T,0,0,0,combined,I'd like to stretch out my wings a little bit too.
Dialogue: 100,0:18:23.99,0:18:26.50,Default,T,0,0,0,split,In my original form.
Dialogue: 100,0:18:33.05,0:18:37.05,Default,K,0,0,0,,As long as you keep things \Non a reasonable level, feel free.
Dialogue: 100,0:18:41.51,0:18:43.10,Default,T,0,0,0,,I'm done!
Dialogue: 100,0:18:45.22,0:18:46.89,Default,K,0,0,0,,Can I take a picture?
Dialogue: 100,0:18:49.06,0:18:49.90,Default,T,0,0,0,,Of course!
Dialogue: 100,0:18:52.52,0:18:55.57,Default,Participant,0,0,0,,Excuse me! Can I get one too?
Dialogue: 100,0:18:55.57,0:18:57.32,Default,Participant,0,0,0,,Oh, me too!
Dialogue: 100,0:19:00.32,0:19:01.82,Default - Top,Participant,0,0,0,,Please look this way for me.
Dialogue: 100,0:19:01.82,0:19:03.66,Default - Top,Participant,0,0,0,,Here too.
Dialogue: 100,0:19:03.12,0:19:05.37,Default,K,0,0,0,,Oh, it's almost time.
Dialogue: 100,0:19:04.53,0:19:06.45,Default - Top,Participant,0,0,0,,Same here.
Dialogue: 100,0:19:06.04,0:19:06.95,Default,K,0,0,0,,I guess it's fine.
Dialogue: 100,0:19:08.21,0:19:09.62,Default,Participant,0,0,0,Split,Hello.
Dialogue: 100,0:19:09.62,0:19:11.33,Default,Participant,0,0,0,Split,I'm here like I said.
Dialogue: 100,0:19:11.33,0:19:12.63,Default,T,0,0,0,,Oh, hello.
Dialogue: 100,0:19:12.63,0:19:14.71,Default,T,0,0,0,,Wait, are you okay?
Dialogue: 100,0:19:14.71,0:19:18.09,Default,Participant,0,0,0,,Well, I'm honestly having a hard time.
Dialogue: 100,0:19:18.09,0:19:19.38,Default,Participant,0,0,0,,But I'll hang in there.
Dialogue: 100,0:19:20.38,0:19:21.64,Default,T,0,0,0,split,Um...
Dialogue: 100,0:19:22.43,0:19:27.47,Default,T,0,0,0,split,I feel like everyone's being drawn here \Nby something powerful.
Dialogue: 100,0:19:28.23,0:19:30.27,Default,T,0,0,0,,Could you tell me what it is?
Dialogue: 100,0:19:34.69,0:19:37.07,Default,Participant,0,0,0,,Let's see...
Dialogue: 100,0:19:37.07,0:19:42.61,Default,Participant,0,0,0,,I think it's something you can \Nonly find right here, right now.
Dialogue: 100,0:19:45.58,0:19:48.79,Default,Participant,0,0,0,,And everyone here loves it.
Dialogue: 100,0:19:58.05,0:19:59.51,Default,T,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 100,0:20:01.01,0:20:03.14,Default,T,0,0,0,,I really know that feeling.
Dialogue: 100,0:20:03.68,0:20:06.26,Default,Participant,0,0,0,combined,Sorry, but could you hurry it up?
Dialogue: 100,0:20:06.26,0:20:08.14,Default,Participant,0,0,0,,Oh, right.
Dialogue: 100,0:20:09.60,0:20:11.64,Default,T,0,0,0,,They've formed another line!
Dialogue: 100,0:20:12.77,0:20:18.61,Default - Italic,Announce,0,0,0,,{\an8}Comic Market 90 is now over.
Dialogue: 100,0:20:18.61,0:20:21.40,Default - Italic,Announce,0,0,0,,{\an8}Thank you for coming, everyone.
Dialogue: 100,0:20:21.70,0:20:24.78,Default - Italic,Announce,0,0,0,,{\an8}We'll see you again this winter!
Dialogue: 100,0:20:27.24,0:20:28.99,Default,T,0,0,0,,I made it back!
Dialogue: 100,0:20:29.66,0:20:31.00,Default,K,0,0,0,Split,Good to see you.
Dialogue: 100,0:20:31.00,0:20:34.12,Default,K,0,0,0,Split,We managed fine without you in the second half.
Dialogue: 100,0:20:34.12,0:20:37.71,Default,T,0,0,0,,Oh, I'm sorry for skipping out.
Dialogue: 100,0:20:37.71,0:20:38.80,Default,K,0,0,0,,It's fine.
Dialogue: 100,0:20:41.97,0:20:43.93,Default,T,0,0,0,,Oh, Fafnir. How did you—
Dialogue: 100,0:20:45.47,0:20:47.30,Default,T,0,0,0,,Not so well, it seems.
Dialogue: 100,0:20:48.26,0:20:51.06,Default,K,0,0,0,,So, thoughts on your first Comiket?
Dialogue: 100,0:20:52.89,0:20:54.52,Default,T,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 100,0:20:58.52,0:21:01.11,Default,T,0,0,0,,I've reaffirmed my love for you!
Dialogue: 100,0:21:04.15,0:21:06.41,Default,Takiya,0,0,0,,Many thanks, Madam Kobayashi and Madam Tohru!
Dialogue: 100,0:21:06.41,0:21:07.87,Default,Takiya,0,0,0,,Many, many thanks!
Dialogue: 100,0:21:07.87,0:21:10.16,Default,Takiya,0,0,0,,I look forward to your assistance this winter too!
Dialogue: 100,0:21:11.16,0:21:13.66,Default,T,0,0,0,,Never again!
Dialogue: 100,0:21:16.12,0:21:18.17,Default,Sahagin,0,0,0,,What should we do for our next doujin?
Dialogue: 100,0:21:18.54,0:21:20.96,Default,Goblin,0,0,0,,One about a girl who's a dragon maid?
Dialogue: 100,0:21:20.96,0:21:22.17,Default,Witch,0,0,0,,Sounds good.
Dialogue: 100,0:21:26.09,0:21:27.64,Default,K,0,0,0,,Independent research?
Dialogue: 100,0:21:28.76,0:21:30.93,Default,Kanna,0,0,0,,For my summer homework.
Dialogue: 100,0:21:30.93,0:21:32.47,Default,Kanna,0,0,0,,What should I do?
Dialogue: 100,0:21:32.47,0:21:34.06,Default,K,0,0,0,split,Well, if you ask me,
Dialogue: 100,0:21:34.06,0:21:36.52,Default,K,0,0,0,split,I think you should research \Nsomething you find fascinating
Dialogue: 100,0:21:36.52,0:21:39.94,Default,K,0,0,0,,and want to know more about.
Dialogue: 100,0:21:39.94,0:21:41.78,Default,Kanna,0,0,0,,Okay. I'll do that.
Dialogue: 100,0:21:46.07,0:21:47.53,Default,K,0,0,0,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 100,0:21:47.78,0:21:49.53,Default,Kanna,0,0,0,,Studying you.
Dialogue: 100,0:23:26.67,0:23:29.76,Default,Takiya,0,0,0,,Kobayashi, Tohru's become a hot topic on the Internet.
Dialogue: 100,0:23:29.76,0:23:30.72,Default,K,0,0,0,,Go figure.
Dialogue: 100,0:23:30.72,0:23:32.72,Default,Takiya,0,0,0,,They were talking about you too,
Dialogue: 100,0:23:32.72,0:23:34.55,Default,Takiya,0,0,0,,calling you a saleswoman with dead-fish eyes.
Dialogue: 100,0:23:34.55,0:23:35.47,Default,K,0,0,0,,Well, {\i1}excuse{\i0} me!
Dialogue: 100,0:23:35.47,0:23:36.89,Default,Takiya,0,0,0,,And saying those eyes turned them on.
Dialogue: 100,0:23:36.89,0:23:38.22,Default,K,0,0,0,,That just gave me chills.
