Dialogue: 10,0:01:01.99,0:01:03.45,OP-E,,0,0,0,fx,{\fad(0,120)\blur4\an5\pos(960.00,148.00)}Tell me, how did I get here?
Dialogue: 10,0:01:03.45,0:01:05.41,OP-E,,0,0,0,fx,{\fad(120,120)\blur4\an5\pos(960.00,148.00)}I only made one tiny-winey mistake
Dialogue: 10,0:01:05.41,0:01:09.12,OP-E,,0,0,0,fx,{\fad(210,0)\blur4\an5\pos(960.00,148.00)}and now I'm at a ta-la-la ta-la-ta total loss
Dialogue: 10,0:01:09.12,0:01:10.62,OP-E,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur4\an5\pos(960.00,148.00)}Why now of all times
Dialogue: 10,0:01:10.62,0:01:12.42,OP-E,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur4\an5\pos(960.00,148.00)}did I grow a spine and stick around?
Dialogue: 10,0:01:12.42,0:01:15.96,OP-E,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur4\an5\pos(960.00,148.00)}Somehow I've been taken by whimsy
Dialogue: 10,0:01:15.96,0:01:18.21,OP-E,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur4\an5\pos(960.00,148.00)}with no choice but to sing along
Dialogue: 10,0:01:18.21,0:01:21.55,OP-E,,0,0,0,fx,{\fad(0,120)\blur4\an5\pos(960.00,148.00)}That's just how it is at first,
Dialogue: 10,0:01:21.55,0:01:25.22,OP-E,,0,0,0,fx,{\fad(300,0)\blur4\an5\pos(960.00,148.00)}feeling like you're not in control
Dialogue: 10,0:01:25.22,0:01:28.77,OP-E,,0,0,0,fx,{\fad(0,120)\blur4\an5\pos(960.00,148.00)}But if you open up and listen...
Dialogue: 10,0:01:28.77,0:01:33.90,OP-E,,0,0,0,fx,{\fad(180,0)\blur4\an5\pos(960.00,148.00)}that's your voice saying, "Come on! Let's go!"
Dialogue: 10,0:01:33.90,0:01:35.65,OP-E,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur4\an5\pos(960.00,148.00)}(Anywhere is fine!)
Dialogue: 10,0:01:35.65,0:01:42.53,OP-E,,0,0,0,fx,{\fad(0,160)\blur4\an5\pos(960.00,148.00)}I have the courage to become your wings
Dialogue: 10,0:01:42.53,0:01:46.08,OP-E,,0,0,0,fx,{\fad(120,120)\blur4\an5\pos(960.00,148.00)}I'll take on the world without any fear
Dialogue: 10,0:01:46.08,0:01:50.00,OP-E,,0,0,0,fx,{\fad(220,0)\blur4\an5\pos(960.00,148.00)}as long as I feel this magic
Dialogue: 10,0:01:50.00,0:01:56.79,OP-E,,0,0,0,fx,{\fad(120,120)\blur4\an5\pos(960.00,148.00)}A bouquet for this unfamiliar world,
Dialogue: 10,0:01:56.79,0:02:00.67,OP-E,,0,0,0,fx,{\fad(170,0)\blur4\an5\pos(960.00,148.00)}wrapped up together in this moment
Dialogue: 10,0:02:00.67,0:02:02.34,OP-E,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur4\an5\pos(960.00,148.00)}We communicate on different levels,
