Comment: 0,0:01:01.99,0:01:03.45,OP-E,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\blur4}Tell me, how did I get here?
Comment: 0,0:01:03.45,0:01:05.41,OP-E,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\blur4}I only made one tiny-winey mistake
Comment: 0,0:01:05.41,0:01:09.12,OP-E,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\blur4}and now I'm at a ta-la-la ta-la-ta total loss
Comment: 0,0:01:09.12,0:01:10.62,OP-E,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\blur4}Why now of all times
Comment: 0,0:01:10.62,0:01:12.42,OP-E,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\blur4}did I grow a spine and stick around?
Comment: 0,0:01:12.42,0:01:15.96,OP-E,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\blur4}Somehow I've been taken by whimsy
Comment: 0,0:01:15.96,0:01:18.21,OP-E,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\blur4}with no choice but to sing along
Comment: 0,0:01:18.21,0:01:21.55,OP-E,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\blur4}That's just how it is at first,
Comment: 0,0:01:21.55,0:01:25.22,OP-E,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\blur4}feeling like you're not in control
Comment: 0,0:01:25.22,0:01:28.77,OP-E,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\blur4}But if you open up and listen...
Comment: 0,0:01:28.77,0:01:33.90,OP-E,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\blur4}that's your voice saying, "Come on! Let's go!"
Comment: 0,0:01:33.90,0:01:35.65,OP-E,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\blur4}(Anywhere is fine!)
Comment: 0,0:01:35.65,0:01:42.53,OP-E,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\blur4}I have the courage to become your wings
Comment: 0,0:01:42.53,0:01:46.08,OP-E,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\blur4}I'll take on the world without any fear
Comment: 0,0:01:46.08,0:01:50.00,OP-E,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\blur4}as long as I feel this magic
Comment: 0,0:01:50.00,0:01:56.79,OP-E,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\blur4}A bouquet for this unfamiliar world,
Comment: 0,0:01:56.79,0:02:00.67,OP-E,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\blur4}wrapped up together in this moment
Comment: 0,0:02:00.67,0:02:02.34,OP-E,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\blur4}We communicate on different levels,
Comment: 0,0:02:02.34,0:02:04.22,OP-E,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\blur4}but it doesn't bother me one bit
Comment: 0,0:02:04.22,0:02:06.64,OP-E,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\blur4}so long as this peace lasts forevermore
