Comment: 0,0:22:15.43,0:22:17.64,ED-E,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\c&H9B48B8&}So sweet and filling
Comment: 0,0:22:17.64,0:22:19.93,ED-E,clipout,0,0,0,karaoke,{\c&H9B48B8&}Pure bliss~ {_ln choose the punctuation}{tildes cuz Tohru's a huge weeb}{ln you clown this is elma} Seconds, please!
Comment: 0,0:22:20.06,0:22:22.23,ED-E,clipin,0,0,0,karaoke,{\c&HF7CD89&}Come on, snuggle with me
Comment: 0,0:22:22.23,0:22:26.32,ED-E,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\c&HF7CD89&}Get over here and quit being a tease!
Comment: 0,0:22:26.52,0:22:28.78,ED-E,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\c&HEBAFE9&}Why must the rules be so strict?
Comment: 0,0:22:28.78,0:22:30.99,ED-E,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\c&HF7CD89&}It's like my heart's bound in chains
Comment: 0,0:22:30.99,0:22:35.45,ED-E,,0,0,0,karaoke,What an inferior and foolish system of values
Comment: 0,0:22:35.45,0:22:37.66,ED-E,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\c&H9B48B8&}It just isn't any good
Comment: 0,0:22:37.66,0:22:39.62,ED-E,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\c&H23AAFF&}These "morals" of yours are worthless
Comment: 0,0:22:39.62,0:22:43.46,ED-E,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\c&H23AAFF&}Ah~ I wanna eradicate it all!
Comment: 0,0:22:44.17,0:22:49.01,ED-E,,0,0,0,karaoke,Let's do some interspecies communication
Comment: 0,0:22:49.01,0:22:53.26,ED-E,,0,0,0,karaoke,and eclipse the world with our passion
Comment: 0,0:22:53.26,0:22:57.89,ED-E,,0,0,0,karaoke,A whole week of that?
Comment: 0,0:22:57.89,0:23:02.48,ED-E,,0,0,0,karaoke,It'd be more precious than an eternity
Comment: 0,0:23:02.48,0:23:05.90,ED-E,,0,0,0,karaoke,The past and the future don't mean a thing
Comment: 0,0:23:05.90,0:23:08.02,ED-E,,0,0,0,karaoke,Simply being here right now
Comment: 0,0:23:08.02,0:23:10.28,ED-E,,0,0,0,karaoke,with the people here right now
Comment: 0,0:23:10.28,0:23:11.24,ED-E,nooffset,0,0,0,karaoke,is what I love!
Comment: 0,0:23:13.41,0:23:15.62,ED-E,,0,0,0,karaoke,interspecies communication
Comment: 0,0:23:17.83,0:23:20.00,ED-E,,0,0,0,karaoke,supersimple imagination
Comment: 0,0:23:20.00,0:23:24.96,ED-E,,0,0,0,karaoke,Eliminate common sense and you're in paradise! Paradise!
